%python

import openapi_client
from openapi_client.rest import ApiException
import time

#Initialization
configuration = openapi_client.configuration.Configuration()
configuration.host = "http://server:8090"
api_instance = openapi_client.ApiClient(configuration)
source_api = openapi_client.SourceApi(api_instance)
pipeline_api = openapi_client.PipelineApi(api_instance)
normal_run_api = openapi_client.PipelineNormalRunApi(api_instance)
exported_table_api = openapi_client.ExportedTablesApi(api_instance)
upload_api = openapi_client.UploadApi(api_instance)

# Create sources: 
####customer
customer_source = openapi_client.Source()
customer_source.source_name = "customer"
customer_source.metadata = {"fluir.spark.format": "csv", "fluir.spark.header": False,
                        "fluir.spark.delimiter": "|",
                        "fluir.spark.path": "/user/root/tpch/customer.tbl", "displayType": "SCP"}
customer_source.data_schema = '{\"type\":\"struct\",\"fields\":[{\"name\":\"C_CUSTKEY\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"C_NAME\",\"type\":\"string\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"C_ADDRESS\",\"type\":\"string\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"C_NATIONKEY\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"C_PHONE\",\"type\":\"string\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"C_ACCTBAL\",\"type\":\"double\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"C_MKTSEGMENT\",\"type\":\"string\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"C_COMMENT\",\"type\":\"string\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}}]}'
customer_source.source_type = "SPARKDATASOURCE"
resp = source_api.create_source("customer", customer_source)
print(resp)

# lineitem
lineitem_source = openapi_client.Source()
lineitem_source.source_name = "lineitem"
lineitem_source.metadata = {"fluir.spark.format": "csv", "fluir.spark.header": False,
                        "fluir.spark.delimiter": "|",
                        "fluir.spark.path": "/user/root/tpch/lineitem.tbl", "displayType": "SCP"}
lineitem_source.data_schema = '{\"type\":\"struct\",\"fields\":[{\"name\":\"L_ORDERKEY\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"L_PARTKEY\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"L_SUPPKEY\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"L_LINENUMBER\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"L_QUANTITY\",\"type\":\"double\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"L_EXTENDEDPRICE\",\"type\":\"double\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"L_DISCOUNT\",\"type\":\"double\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"L_TAX\",\"type\":\"double\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"L_RETURNFLAG\",\"type\":\"string\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"L_LINESTATUS\",\"type\":\"string\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"L_SHIPDATE\",\"type\":\"date\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"L_COMMITDATE\",\"type\":\"date\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"L_RECEIPTDATE\",\"type\":\"date\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"L_SHIPINSTRUCT\",\"type\":\"string\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"L_SHIPMODE\",\"type\":\"string\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"L_COMMENT\",\"type\":\"string\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}}]}'
lineitem_source.source_type = "SPARKDATASOURCE"
resp = source_api.create_source("lineitem", lineitem_source)
print(resp)

# nation
nation_source = openapi_client.Source()
nation_source.source_name = "nation"
nation_source.metadata = {"fluir.spark.format": "csv", "fluir.spark.header": False,
                      "fluir.spark.delimiter": "|",
                      "fluir.spark.path": "/user/root/tpch/nation.tbl", "displayType": "SCP"}
nation_source.data_schema = '{\"type\":\"struct\",\"fields\":[{\"name\":\"N_NATIONKEY\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"N_NAME\",\"type\":\"string\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"N_REGIONKEY\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"N_COMMENT\",\"type\":\"string\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}}]}'

# orders

                      "fluir.spark.delimiter": "|",
                      "fluir.spark.path": "/user/root/tpch/orders.tbl", "displayType": "SCP"}
orders_source.data_schema = '{\"type\":\"struct\",\"fields\":[{\"name\":\"O_ORDERKEY\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"O_CUSTKEY\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"O_ORDERSTATUS\",\"type\":\"string\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"O_TOTALPRICE\",\"type\":\"double\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"O_ORDERDATE\",\"type\":\"date\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"O_ORDERPRIORITY\",\"type\":\"string\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"O_CLERK\",\"type\":\"string\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"O_SHIPPRIORITY\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"O_COMMENT\",\"type\":\"string\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}}]}'
orders_source.source_type = "SPARKDATASOURCE"

# part
part_source = openapi_client.Source()
part_source.source_name = "part"
part_source.metadata = {"fluir.spark.format": "csv", "fluir.spark.header": False,

part_source.data_schema = '{\"type\":\"struct\",\"fields\":[{\"name\":\"P_PARTKEY\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"P_NAME\",\"type\":\"string\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"P_MFGR\",\"type\":\"string\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"P_BRAND\",\"type\":\"string\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"P_TYPE\",\"type\":\"string\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"P_SIZE\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"P_CONTAINER\",\"type\":\"string\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"P_RETAILPRICE\",\"type\":\"double\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"P_COMMENT\",\"type\":\"string\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}}]}'
part_source.source_type = "SPARKDATASOURCE"
resp = source_api.create_source("part", part_source)
print(resp)

# partsupp
partsupp_source = openapi_client.Source()
partsupp_source.source_name = "partsupp"
partsupp_source.metadata = {"fluir.spark.format": "csv", "fluir.spark.header": False,
                        "fluir.spark.delimiter": "|",
                        "fluir.spark.path": "/user/root/tpch/partsupp.tbl", "displayType": "SCP"}
partsupp_source.data_schema = '{\"type\":\"struct\",\"fields\":[{\"name\":\"PS_PARTKEY\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"PS_SUPPKEY\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"PS_AVAILQTY\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"PS_SUPPLYCOST\",\"type\":\"double\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"PS_COMMENT\",\"type\":\"string\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}}]}'

region_source = openapi_client.Source()

region_source.metadata = {"fluir.spark.format": "csv", "fluir.spark.header": False,

region_source.data_schema = '{\"type\":\"struct\",\"fields\":[{\"name\":\"R_REGIONKEY\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"R_NAME\",\"type\":\"string\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"name\":\"R_COMMENT\",\"type\":\"string\",\"nullable\":false,\"metadata\":{}}]}'

%python
# create tpch pipeline
pipelineBody = openapi_client.PipelineMetadata()
pipelineBody.auto_schema_refresh = "true"
pipelineBody.description = "TPCH data application"
resp = pipeline_api.create_pipeline("tpchpipeline", pipelineBody)
print(resp)

# add nodes in pipeline
source_node = openapi_client.SourceNode(source="customer", configuration=configuration)
resp = pipeline_api.add_source_node("tpchpipeline", "customer", source_node)
print(resp)
query = "select * from nation, region where nation.N_REGIONKEY = region.R_REGIONKEY"
processor_node = openapi_client.ProcessorNode(metadata={}, query=query)
resp = pipeline_api.add_processor_node("tpchpipeline", "nationregion", processor_node)
print(resp)

query = "select * from customer, nationregion where customer.C_NATIONKEY = nationregion.N_NATIONKEY".upper()
processor_node = openapi_client.ProcessorNode(metadata={}, query=query)
resp = pipeline_api.add_processor_node("tpchpipeline", "custnationregion", processor_node)
print(resp)

query = "select S_SUPPKEY as S_SUPPKEY, S_NAME as S_NAME, S_ADDRESS as S_ADDRESS, S_PHONE as S_PHONE, S_ACCTBAL as S_ACCTBAL, S_COMMENT as S_COMMENT, N_NAME as S_NATION, R_NAME as S_REGION from supplier, nationregion where supplier.S_NATIONKEY = nationregion.N_NATIONKEY".upper()
processor_node = openapi_client.ProcessorNode(metadata={}, query=query)
resp = pipeline_api.add_processor_node("tpchpipeline", "suppnationregion", processor_node)
print(resp)

query = "select * from part, partsupp where part.P_PARTKEY = partsupp.PS_PARTKEY"
processor_node = openapi_client.ProcessorNode(metadata={}, query=query)
resp = pipeline_api.add_processor_node("tpchpipeline", "partpartsupp", processor_node)
print(resp)

query = "select * from suppnationregion, partpartsupp where suppnationregion.S_SUPPKEY = partpartsupp.PS_SUPPKEY".upper()
processor_node = openapi_client.ProcessorNode(metadata={}, query=query)
resp = pipeline_api.add_processor_node("tpchpipeline", "supppartpartsupp", processor_node)
print(resp)

query = "select * from custnationregion, orders where custnationregion.C_CUSTKEY = orders.O_CUSTKEY"
processor_node = openapi_client.ProcessorNode(metadata={}, query=query)
resp = pipeline_api.add_processor_node("tpchpipeline", "custorder", processor_node)
print(resp)

query = "select * from supppartpartsupp, lineitem where supppartpartsupp.PS_PARTKEY = lineitem.L_PARTKEY AND supppartpartsupp.PS_SUPPKEY = lineitem.L_SUPPKEY".upper()
processor_node = openapi_client.ProcessorNode(metadata={}, query=query)
resp = pipeline_api.add_processor_node("tpchpipeline", "supplierlineitem", processor_node)
print(resp)

query = "select * from supplierlineitem, custorder where supplierlineitem.L_ORDERKEY = custorder.O_ORDERKEY"
processor_node = openapi_client.ProcessorNode(metadata={}, query=query)
resp = pipeline_api.add_processor_node("tpchpipeline", "custorderlineitem", processor_node)
print(resp)

%python
# TPC-H query-1: Calculate the pricing summary report
query = "select l_returnflag, l_linestatus, sum(l_quantity) as sum_qty, sum(l_extendedprice) as sum_base_price, sum(l_extendedprice*(1-l_discount)) as sum_disc_price, sum(l_extendedprice*(1-l_discount)*(1+l_tax)) as sum_charge, avg(l_quantity) as avg_qty, avg(l_extendedprice) as avg_price, avg(l_discount) as avg_disc, count(*) as count_order from custorderlineitem_sink where l_shipdate < \"1998-09-01\" group by l_returnflag, l_linestatus order by l_returnflag, l_linestatus"

resp = normal_run_api.analyze_sink_data("tpchpipeline", query)
print(resp)

%python
# TPC-H query-2: Calculate top revenue orders
query = "select  o_orderkey,  sum(l_extendedprice*(1-l_discount)) as revenue, o_orderdate,  o_shippriority  from  custorderlineitem_sink where  c_mktsegment = \"BUILDING\" and o_orderdate < \"1995-03-15\" and l_shipdate > \"1995-03-15\"  group by o_orderkey,  o_orderdate,  o_shippriority order by  revenue desc, o_orderdate  limit 1"

resp = normal_run_api.analyze_sink_data("tpchpipeline", query)
print(resp)

# TPC-H query-3: Check order priorities
query = "select o_orderpriority, count(distinct o_orderkey) as order_count  from custorderlineitem_sink where o_orderdate < \"1993-10-01\" and o_orderdate >= \"1993-07-01\" and l_commitdate < l_receiptdate group by o_orderpriority  order by o_orderpriority"

resp = normal_run_api.analyze_sink_data("tpchpipeline", query)
print(resp)

%python
# TPC-H query-4: Calculate Nation wise revenue
query = "select s_nation, sum(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount)) as revenue  from custorderlineitem_sink where s_region = \"ASIA\" and o_orderdate >= \"1994-01-01\" and o_orderdate < \"1995-01-01\" group by s_nation  order by revenue desc"

resp = normal_run_api.analyze_sink_data("tpchpipeline", query)
print(resp)

%python
# TPC-H query-5: calculate total reveenue between particular shipping dates
query = "select sum(l_extendedprice*l_discount) as revenue from custorderlineitem_sink where l_shipdate >= \"1994-01-01\" and l_shipdate < \"1995-01-01\" and l_discount between 0.06 - 0.01 and 0.06 + 0.01 and l_quantity < 24"

resp = normal_run_api.analyze_sink_data("tpchpipeline", query)
print(resp)

%python
# TPC-H query-6: Calculate France and Germany's total revenue
query = "select s_nation,  n_name, year(l_shipdate) as l_year, sum(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount)) as revenue from custorderlineitem_sink where ((s_nation = \"FRANCE\" and  n_name = \"GERMANY\") or ( n_name = \"FRANCE\" and s_nation = \"GERMANY\")) group by s_nation,  n_name, year(l_shipdate)  order by s_nation,  n_name, l_year"

resp = normal_run_api.analyze_sink_data("tpchpipeline", query)
print(resp)

%python
# TPC-H query-7: Calculate India's yearly market share
query = "select year(o_orderdate) as o_year, sum(case when s_nation = \"INDIA\" then l_extendedprice * (1-l_discount) else 0 end) / sum(l_extendedprice * (1-l_discount)) as mkt_share from custorderlineitem_sink where r_name = \"ASIA\" and p_type = \"LARGE BURNISHED BRASS\" and o_orderdate >= \"1993-01-01\" and o_orderdate <= \"1996-12-31\" group by year(o_orderdate) order by o_year"

resp = normal_run_api.analyze_sink_data("tpchpipeline", query)
print(resp)

%python
# TPC-H query-8: Calculate Yearly profit of almond suppliers nation wise
query = "select s_nation, year(o_orderdate) as o_year, sum(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount) - ps_supplycost * l_quantity) as sum_profit from custorderlineitem_sink where p_name like \"%almond%\" group by s_nation, year(o_orderdate) order by s_nation, o_year"

resp = normal_run_api.analyze_sink_data("tpchpipeline", query)
print(resp)

%python
# TPC-H query-9: Calculate per cusyto
query = "select c_name, c_acctbal, n_name, c_address, c_phone, c_comment, sum(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount)) as revenue from custorderlineitem_sink where   o_orderdate >= \"1993-10-01\" and    o_orderdate < \"1994-01-01\" and   l_returnflag = \"R\" group by c_name, c_acctbal, n_name, c_address, c_phone, c_comment order by revenue desc"

resp = normal_run_api.analyze_sink_data("tpchpipeline", query)
print(resp)
